# Use PHP 8.1
AddHandler application/x-httpd-ea-php81 .php

# CodeIgniter URL Rewriting
RewriteEngine On

# Allow these files to run directly (BEFORE the main rule)
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} ^/install\.php$ [OR]
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} ^/diagnose\.php$
RewriteRule ^ - [L]

# Remove index.php from URLs
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php/$1 [L]

# Protect sensitive directories
<FilesMatch "^\.">
    Order allow,deny
    Deny from all
</FilesMatch>

# MIME types for audio files
AddType audio/mpeg mp3
AddType audio/mp4 m4a
AddType audio/ogg ogg
AddType audio/wav wav
AddType audio/flac flac
```

The key change is using `RewriteRule ^ - [L]` which says "stop processing and serve the file directly" for `install.php` and `diagnose.php`.

